msgid "3. Udāyivagga "
msgstr "3. With Udāyī "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 23. Ṭhāniyasutta → ṭhānasuttaṃ (bj) | ṭhānā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn46.23:0.3"
msgid "23. Ṭhāniyasutta "
msgstr "23. Grounds "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.84, sc1
msgctxt "sn46.23:1.1"
msgid "“Kāmarāgaṭṭhāniyānaṃ, bhikkhave, dhammānaṃ manasikārabahulīkārā anuppanno ceva kāmacchando uppajjati, uppanno ca kāmacchando bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, when you frequently attend improperly to things that are grounds for sensual greed, sensual desire arises, and once arisen it increases and grows. "

msgctxt "sn46.23:1.2"
msgid "Byāpādaṭṭhāniyānaṃ, bhikkhave, dhammānaṃ manasikārabahulīkārā anuppanno ceva byāpādo uppajjati, uppanno ca byāpādo bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "When you frequently attend improperly to things that are grounds for ill will, ill will arises, and once arisen it increases and grows. "

msgctxt "sn46.23:1.3"
msgid "Thinamiddhaṭṭhāniyānaṃ, bhikkhave, dhammānaṃ manasikārabahulīkārā anuppannañceva thinamiddhaṃ uppajjati, uppannañca thinamiddhaṃ bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "When you frequently attend improperly to things that are grounds for dullness and drowsiness, dullness and drowsiness arise, and once arisen they increase and grow. "

msgctxt "sn46.23:1.4"
msgid "Uddhaccakukkuccaṭṭhāniyānaṃ, bhikkhave, dhammānaṃ manasikārabahulīkārā anuppannañceva uddhaccakukkuccaṃ uppajjati, uppannañca uddhaccakukkuccaṃ bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "When you frequently attend improperly to things that are grounds for restlessness and remorse, restlessness and remorse arise, and once arisen they increase and grow. "

msgctxt "sn46.23:1.5"
msgid "Vicikicchāṭṭhāniyānaṃ, bhikkhave, dhammānaṃ manasikārabahulīkārā anuppannā ceva vicikicchā uppajjati, uppannā ca vicikicchā bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "When you frequently attend improperly to things that are grounds for doubt, doubt arises, and once arisen it increases and grows. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn46.23:2.1"
msgid "Satisambojjhaṅgaṭṭhāniyānaṃ, bhikkhave, dhammānaṃ manasikārabahulīkārā anuppanno ceva satisambojjhaṅgo uppajjati, uppanno ca satisambojjhaṅgo bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati … pe … "
msgstr "When you frequently attend properly on things that are grounds for the awakening factor of mindfulness, the awakening factor of mindfulness arises, and once arisen it’s fully developed. … "

msgctxt "sn46.23:2.2"
msgid "upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṭṭhāniyānaṃ, bhikkhave, dhammānaṃ manasikārabahulīkārā anuppanno ceva upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo uppajjati, uppanno ca upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchatī”ti. "
msgstr "When you frequently attend properly on things that are grounds for the awakening factor of equanimity, the awakening factor of equanimity arises, and once arisen it’s fully developed.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.23:2.3"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

